{
  "stem": "3952.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had who to hold onto, and that's what saved me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's the only way I can explain that I got 25 without a-- without a--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It reminds me of a little episode from Wolfsberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were working in Wolfsberg the first day, and I come out to work, and we were-- they were putting these cement sacks. 25 kilos-- that's like what? 50, 55 pounds, 60 pounds-- on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would fall underneath the bag-- the bag.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So and-- and then came that-- that non-German, the meister, the foreman, came and put this hand-- hand to my heart, and he found that it's beating like hell.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's beating like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he said, go there behind the-- there were some planks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stay there and rest a little and have a-- and he tells somebody, give him a glass of tea.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sure enough, the largerkommandant walks by and sees somebody stays there is not working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he comes over, puts his hand like Napoleon, here, and he says to me, what is it, junge?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What do you have?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, my heart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My heart.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I put my hand, and I-- and he says, yeah, your heart.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly, he gives me a [INAUDIBLE] on both-- with both hands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the blood starts running from my nose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SPEAKS GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I took that sack, and I started running with it like nobody else could run.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So to show you what fear can do to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember another episode now that I talk about that fellow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That Kommandant was a [SPEAKS GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like a sergeant-major.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We called him the shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why the shoemaker?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he would-- he would-- he would look at-- you had wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
